{"id":223,"parent_id":222,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":223,"title":"Philemon 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Philem.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1","content":[["div",[".title","The Epistle of Paul to",["br"],["span.dominant","Philemon"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","The gospel changes a servant into a brother."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.1","order":"03.20.001.23282"},["b","1"],"Paul, a prisoner of Jesus Christ, and Timothy",["i","our"],"brother, unto Philemon our dearly beloved, and fellowlabourer,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.2","order":"03.20.001.23283"},["b","2"],"And to",["i","our"],"beloved Apphia, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Archippus"],"our fellowsoldier, and to the church in thy house:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.3","order":"03.20.001.23284"},["b","3"],"Grace to you, and peace, from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.4","order":"03.20.001.23285"},["b","4"],"I thank my God, making mention of thee always in my prayers,"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.5","order":"03.20.001.23286"},["b","5"],"Hearing of thy love and faith, which thou hast toward the Lord Jesus, and toward all saints;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.6","order":"03.20.001.23287"},["b","6"],"That the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"communication"],"of thy faith may become",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"effectual"],"by the acknowledging of every good thing which is in you in Christ Jesus."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.7","order":"03.20.001.23288"},["b","7"],"For we have great joy and consolation in thy love, because the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"bowels"],"of the saints are refreshed by thee, brother."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.8","order":"03.20.001.23289"},["b","8"],"Wherefore, though I might be much bold in Christ to enjoin thee that which is convenient,"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.9","order":"03.20.001.23290"},["b","9"],"Yet for love’s sake I rather beseech",["i","thee,"],"being such an one as Paul the aged, and now also a prisoner of Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.10","order":"03.20.001.23291"},["b","10"],"I beseech thee for my son",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Onesimus"],", whom I have begotten in my bonds:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.11","order":"03.20.001.23292"},["b","11"],"Which in time past was to thee unprofitable, but now profitable to thee and to me:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.12","order":"03.20.001.23293"},["b","12"],"Whom I have sent again: thou therefore receive him, that is, mine own bowels:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.13","order":"03.20.001.23294"},["b","13"],"Whom I would have retained with me, that in thy stead he might have ministered unto me in the bonds of the gospel:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.14","order":"03.20.001.23295"},["b","14"],"But without thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"mind"],"would I do nothing; that thy benefit should not be as it were of necessity, but willingly."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.15","order":"03.20.001.23296"},["b","15"],"For perhaps he therefore departed for a season, that thou shouldest receive him for ever;"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.16","order":"03.20.001.23297"},["b","16"],"Not now as a servant, but above a servant, a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"brother"],"beloved, specially to me, but how much more unto thee, both in the flesh, and in the Lord?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.17","order":"03.20.001.23298"},["b","17"],"If thou count me therefore a partner, receive him as myself."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.18","order":"03.20.001.23299"},["b","18"],"If he hath wronged thee, or oweth",["i","thee"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"ought"],", put that on mine account;"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.19","order":"03.20.001.23300"},["b","19"],"I Paul have written",["i","it"],"with mine own hand, I will repay",["i","it:"],"albeit I do not say to thee how thou owest unto me even thine own self besides."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.20","order":"03.20.001.23301"},["b","20"],"Yea, brother, let me have joy of thee in the Lord: refresh my bowels in the Lord."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.21","order":"03.20.001.23302"},["b","21"],"Having confidence in thy obedience I wrote unto thee, knowing that thou wilt also do more than I say."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.22","order":"03.20.001.23303"},["b","22"],"But withal prepare me also a lodging: for I trust that through your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"prayers"],"I shall be given unto you."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.23","order":"03.20.001.23304"},["b","23"],"There salute thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"Epaphras"],", my fellowprisoner in Christ Jesus;"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.24","order":"03.20.001.23305"},["b","24"],"Marcus, Aristarchus,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"Demas"],", Lucas, my fellowlabourers."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.25","order":"03.20.001.23306"},["b","25"],"The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ",["i","be"],"with your spirit. Amen."]],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem.closing.13","order":".000.23329"},[".closing","¶Written from Rome to Philemon, by Onesimus a servant."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.2a","order":"03.20.001.23307"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.17"},"Col. 4:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.6a","order":"03.20.001.23309"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"participation, fellowship."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.6b","order":"03.20.001.23311"},["b","6b"],["span.small","GR"],"active."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.7a","order":"03.20.001.23313"},["b","7a"],["span.small","GR"],"affections, compassion."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.10a","order":"03.20.001.23315"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.9"},"Col. 4:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.14a","order":"03.20.001.23317"},["b","14a"],["span.small","GR"],"assent, suggestion.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mind"},"TG Mind"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.16a","order":"03.20.001.23319"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/brotherhood-and-sisterhood"},"TG Brotherhood and Sisterhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.18a","order":"03.20.001.23321"},["b","18a"],["span.small","GR"],"something, anything."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.22a","order":"03.20.001.23323"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.11"},"2 Cor. 1:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.19"},"Philip. 1:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.23a","order":"03.20.001.23325"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/1.7.7-8"},"Col. 1:7 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.12.12-13"},"4:12 (12–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.24a","order":"03.20.001.23327"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/4.14"},"Col. 4:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/4.10"},"2 Tim. 4:10"],"."]]}
